{"tid":1228252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烈士捐軀，並唔係想更多人絕望，而係想大家一齊還佢一個心願！","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:17:01.000Z","uid":131691,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9d235e6af9797078e72ffce5392e3d9d96cae1","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有兄弟被迫害致死<br />\n傷心係必然嘅<br />\n但係佢會想香港人更加絕望咩？<br />\n唔好畀佢枉死，尊重烈士嘅意願<br />\n今晚眼淚過後，就係明天無比嘅憤怒，無比嘅仇恨<br />\n烈士嘅寶血已經灌溉咗香港大地<br />\n香港人心中反抗嘅火種<br />\n聽日開始，要變成熊熊烈火<br />\n燒清極權嘅欺壓<br />\n還香港一個淨土<br />\n還烈士一個心願</span></strong>"},{"pid":"7657ccb1eb4b0c76df73e8cc339401ef2815ad1f","tid":1228252,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"長期抗爭，永不忘記"},{"pid":"cd7a1f53e47a65403f898d151eb667fb06086d55","tid":1228252,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記義士"},{"pid":"62fdddd0921b591e9da9e195fa1b38826bad5b79","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Aep3pe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Aep3pe.png&h=3a30885d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7667b0dc7561658b1e457eee3592c565d2e56cea","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲<br />\n瞓唔着"},{"pid":"8ad9547b79b1f7b68f8c62786c495c4580c3e36e","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd7a1f53e47a65403f898d151eb667fb06086d55","tid":1228252,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記義士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"永不忘記<br />\n永垂不朽"},{"pid":"0867ffce84617087ae31ae80ea54cabb279043b2","tid":1228252,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:53:27.000Z","msg":"林鄭想還果個女仔公道同佢父母交代, 幫佢出頭<br />\n而家邊個同太古廣場個烈士出頭,同個男仔父母交代<br />\n試問邊個應該同香港市民交代,同呢兩星期上街既香港人出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為個女仔要賠上整個香港, 無視103萬人上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00f2c52c9dc71261f0d171d9da643c47c500c68","tid":1228252,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"烈士叫咩名<br />\n我要記住佢"},{"pid":"0bb6bc7ceaaa690256b348e80f4187fb0b2d7ce1","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00f2c52c9dc71261f0d171d9da643c47c500c68","tid":1228252,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"烈士叫咩名<br />\n我要記住佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"未知"},{"pid":"1d933450423933f07da34ad6183f5798ab2691f8","tid":1228252,"uid":97389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"想最快得到同狗/解放軍對等戰力的方法. 郭文貴講佐啦: 捉混入狗隻中的解放軍/武警出來. 美國需要<span style=\"color: red;\">確實証據證明支共插手介入香港事務</span>. 咁就可以明正言順介入, 到時你哋班&quot;義勇軍&quot;咪合情合理合法咁, 要出乜嘢裝有乜嘢裝攞. <br />\n仲有捉佢哋出來你哋不但冇犯法, 而且仲係幫助維護法紀:<span style=\"color: red;\"> 冒警係嚴重刑事罪行</span>. <br />\n千萬唔好被憤怒控制住, 自己有勇無謀咁去做報復行為. 君子復仇, 十年未晚. 這場仗的最後勝利, 先能讓犠牲者無白費到."},{"pid":"7edd6ca65b55c229ab31d2fcdc00d5cee359e0be","tid":1228252,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:16:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4911f65bcaee843d1b204f6292d48ebd51e4ed70","tid":1228252,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93f5c351dc9c0f25e8a1e823418b890ba7cea0fd","tid":1228252,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}